# Global API Keys Configuration
# ==============================
# This file serves as a template for configuring LLM API keys.
#
# To use:
#   1. Copy this file to 'global.env' in the same directory
#   2. Uncomment and set the API keys you need
#   3. Rebuild the Docker image: make build
#
# API keys set here become the defaults for ALL agents.
# Per-agent keys can override these (see manage-api-keys.sh).
#
# Security notes:
#   - Do NOT commit global.env to version control
#   - Keys are stored with mode 600 (root-only inside container)
#   - Agents can read their keys but cannot modify them

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic (Claude)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenAI (GPT models)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google (Gemini)
