# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GitHub (gh CLI and git HTTPS authentication)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GITHUB_TOKEN is used by git for HTTPS auth and by gh CLI.
# GH_TOKEN is the gh CLI's preferred variable (takes precedence).
# Only one is needed — GH_TOKEN is recommended.
#GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...
#GH_TOKEN=ghp_...

